name: Bulbasaur
description: Bulbasaur is a dual-type Plant/Poison Pokémon introduced in Generation I.
It evolves into Ivysaur starting at level 16, which evolves into Venusaur starting at level 32.

name: Charmander
description: Charmander is a Fire-type Pokémon introduced in Generation I.
It evolves into Charmeleon starting at level 16, which evolves into Charizard starting at level 36.

name: Squirtle
description: Squirtle is a Water-type Pokémon introduced in Generation I.
It evolves into Wartortle starting at level 16, which evolves into Blastoise starting at level 36.

name: Pichu
description: Pikachu is an Electric-type Pokémon introduced in Generation I.
It evolves from Pichu when leveled up with high friendship and evolves into Raichu when exposed to a Thunder Stone.

name: Birsh
description: A bird that, like mammals such as dolphins, adapted to live in seas like fishes. Birsh is also known as "the aquatic Birdumont".
It adapted to live 24/7 in the water by creating an air bubble that also protects their tamers when traveling underwater; this air bubble is created by a symbiosis with another tamigucho.
